{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"699","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"疫情重創經濟 ／世銀：疫情恐使6000萬人陷赤貧 估今年經濟萎縮5%","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/05/20 15:11</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 501px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>中國在武漢肺炎疫情衝擊下，薪資較低、工作經驗在<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>年間的勞工，面臨較高的失業風險。圖為上海街頭的清道夫。中央社記者沈朋達上海攝<span lang='EN-US'>109</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>18</span>日</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社華盛頓<span lang='EN-US'>19</span>日綜合外電報導）世界銀行總裁馬爾帕斯（<span lang='EN-US'>David Malpass</span>）今天警告，冠狀病毒危機恐使大約<span lang='EN-US'>6000</span>萬人陷入赤貧，今年全球經濟恐將萎縮<span lang='EN-US'>5%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>馬爾帕斯說，世銀承諾在未來<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>個月內動支<span lang='EN-US'>1600</span>億美元緊急援助資金，協助各國應對危機，目前已向<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>個國家的援助計畫提供資金。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>馬爾帕斯在電話會議中說：「那（<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>個國家）占世界人口的<span lang='EN-US'>70%</span>。這代表了一個重大里程碑。」</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>馬爾帕斯說，世銀估計<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年全球經濟將萎縮<span lang='EN-US'>5%</span>，將對全球最貧窮國家帶來嚴峻衝擊。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>馬爾帕斯說：「我們估計有多達<span lang='EN-US'>6000</span>萬人將陷入赤貧，抹煞世銀過去<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>年在扶貧方面的成果。我們預測，全球經濟將陷入嚴重衰退。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中國去年底爆發<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>冠狀病毒疾病（<span lang='EN-US'>COVID-19</span>）以來，全球迄今已有近<span lang='EN-US'>500</span>萬人受到感染，超過<span lang='EN-US'>30</span>萬人病故。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>截至目前，世銀已支出<span lang='EN-US'>55</span>億美元，協助貧窮國家鞏固陷入困境的衛生系統、經濟和社會服務。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>不過，馬爾帕斯強調，光靠世銀的努力還不夠，並敦促捐助國加強對貧窮國家提供雙邊援助，以確保經濟持久復甦。（譯者：劉文瑜<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>核稿：嚴思祺）<span lang='EN-US'>1090520</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>:https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202005200126.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-05-22","clk_count":"159"}},"__N_SSG":true}